data.name: label7.Text
data.value: Users agree to: • Provide accurate and complete information when using the system • Use Gabasa only for lawful, educational, and intended purposes • Respect library policies related to borrowing, reservations, and digital access Unauthorized use, misuse of resources, or attempts to compromise system integrity may result in access suspension.

data.name: label5.Text
data.value: Gabasa is a digital library and reading management system designed to provide access to physical and digital library resources, manage borrowing and reservations, and support academic and educational use.
